SIMPLE: loveless
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Loveless
<hw>Love"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Void of love; void of
tenderness or kindness.</def> <rj><au>Milton. Shelton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not attracting love; unattractive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>These are ill-favored to see to; and yet, as <qex>loveless</qex>
as they be, they are not without some medicinable virtues.</q>
<rj><qau>Holland.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lovelily</ent>⟦br⟧
